address2: Opposite Andheri Fire Station S.V. Road, Andheri (West)
longBusinessSummary: Visagar Polytex Limited engages in the design, manufacture, wholesale, retail, and trade of textiles in India. The company offers ethnic wear, including sarees, lehengas, and suits; interlining goods; and various fabrics. It operates a retail chain that offers apparel and ethnic wear under the Vividha brand. Visagar Polytex Limited was incorporated in 1983 and is based in Mumbai, India.
